MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-845. Duffy v. State Auto. Mut. Ins. Co.

Cuyahoga County, No. 67061. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective December 6, 1995.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
